text: Kateřina Kramperová and Bernarda Pera were the defending champions, but Pera chose not to participate. Kramperová partnered Amandine Hesse, but they lost in the first round. Demi Schuurs and Renata Voráčová won the title, defeating Sílvia Soler Espinosa and Sara Sorribes Tormo in the final, 7–5, 3–6, [10–4]. == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Advantage Cars Prague Open - Doubles Category:Advantage Cars Prague Open
